cia\" 2013-06-03]\n* [http://www.mindfood.com/gallery/55th-la-biennale-of-venice-gallery-images/visitor-walks-past-an-installation-called-campo-de-color-by-bolivian-artist-sonia-falcone-during-the-55th-la-biennale-of-venice/ \"Installacion called Campos De Color\" 2013-06-04]\n* [http://www.abc.net.au/arts/blog/2013-venice-biennale/default.htm \"Highlights from the 2013 Venice Biennale\" 2013-06-04]\n* [http://artbusinessnews.com/2013/06/venice-biennale-showcases-art-from-88-countries/ \"Venice Biennale showcases art from 88 countries\" 2013-06-05]\n* [http://premium.lefigaro.fr/arts-expositions/2013/06/04/03015-20130604ARTFIG00231-une-biennale-de-venise-sans-limite-d-age.php \"Une Biennale de Venise sans limite d'\u00e2ge\" 2013-06-06]\n* [http://www.fashionoffice.org/culture/2013/biennalevenice-spicy6-2013.htm \"The Spiciest Installation!\" 2013-06]\n* [http://www.parismatch.com/People/Spectacles/En-images/Soiree-Sonia-Falcone-Que-c-est-glamour-Venise-518199 \"Soir\u00e9e Sonia Falcone Que c'est glamour Venise!\" 2013-06-12]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150923174215/http://www.artishock.cl/2013/06/14/cartografias-para-un-nuevo-mundo/ \"Cartografias para un nuevo mundo\" 2013-06-14]\n* [http://www.la-razon.com/index.php?_url=/suplementos/tendencias/Sonia-Falcone-tiende-campo-Venecia_0_1859814150.html \"Sonia Falcone tiende un campo de color en Venecia\" 2013-06-30]\n* [http://eju.tv/2013/07/sonia-montero-maestra-del-estilo/ \"Sonia Montero, maestra del estilo\" 2013-07-06]\n* [http://www.bonews.org/noticia/133887/sonia-falcone-una-artista-solidaria-y-silenciosa \"Sonia Falcone, Una artista solidaria y silenciosa\" 2013-07-14]\n* [http://www.lavozdelsandinismo.com/cultura/2013-08-08/pintora-boliviana-sonia-falcone-presenta-atractiva-obra-en-bienal-de-venecia/ \"Pintora Boliviana Sonia Falcone presenta atractiva obra en Bienal de Venecia\" 2013-08-08]\n* [http://www.cassone-art.com/magazine/article/2013/08/the-treasures-of-the-world-in-venice-2013/?psrc=perspectives \"The treasures of the world in Venice 2013\" 2013-08]\n* [http://en.sib.fm/oftheweek/2013/09/18/spices-of-the-week \"Spices of the week\" 2013-09-09]\n* [http://revistas.elheraldo.co/latitud/la-55a-bienal-de-venecia-el-deseo-quimerico-del-arte-actual-128258 \"La 55th Bienal de Venecia, el deseo qu\u00edmerico del arte actual\" 2013-10-12]\n* [http://artdistricts.com/psh-projects-the-new-art-dealers/ \"PSH, Projects the new art dealers\" 2013-10]\n* [http://www.elperiodicomediterraneo.com/noticias/cuadernos/arte-la-serenissima_848122.html \"Arte la serenissima\" 2013-11-24]\n* [http://www.paginasiete.bo/cultura/2013/12/28/obra-falcone-brillo-feria-arte-moscu-9823.html \"Obra de Sonia Falcone brill\u00f3 en la feria de arte de Mosc\u00fa\" 2013-12-28]\n* [http://www.lapatriaenlinea.com/?nota=168064 \"Sonia Falcone exhibe su obra en Mosc\u00fa con Damien Hirst\" 2013-12-27]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143640/http://www.lostiempos.com/lecturas/artes-plasticas/artes-plasticas/20131229/sonia-falcone-en-rusia-junto-a-hirst_240097_522053.html \"Sonia Falcone en Rusia junto a Damien Hirst\" 2013-12-30]\n* [http://www.eldia.com.bo/mobile.php?cat=356&pla=7&id_articulo=135212 \"Sonia Falcone en obras de exportaci\u00f3n\" 2013-12-30]\n* [http://www.french-riviera-tendances.org/index.php?option=com_phocagallery&view=category&id=938:vernissage-de-l-exposition-de-damien-hirst-et-sonia-falcone-societe-generale-monaco-le-9-janvier-2014 \"Vernissage de l'exposition de Damien Hirst et Sonia Falcone\" 2014-01-09]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20140608100756/http://arte.elpais.com.uy/lanzamiento-de-la-bienal-de-montevideo-2014/#.VWcAujm9YlI \"Lanzamiento de la Bienal de Montevideo\" 2014-01-24]\n* [http://www.royalmonaco.net/article-monaco-arte-vernissage-sonia-falcone-122277127.html \"Monaco arte: Vernissage Sonia Falcone\" 2014-01-27]\n* [http://hoybolivia.com/Especial.php?IdEspecial=11257 \"Sonia Falcone en M\u00f3naco\" 2014-02-11]\n* [http://www.opinion.com.bo/opinion/ar