k.com/rickygervais Gervais' video interview on Big Think]\n* [http://kempton.wordpress.com/2010/06/24/ricky-gervais-sir-peter-ustinov-award-for-comedy-2010-banff-world-tv-festival/ Video interview & acceptance speech of Ricky Gervais winning Sir Peter Ustinov Award for Comedy @2010 Banff World TV Festival]\n\n==External links==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{Wikiquote|The Ricky Gervais Show}}\n{{Commons category|Ricky Gervais}}\n* {{Official Website|http://www.rickygervais.com}}\n* {{IMDb name|315041}}\n* {{Rotten-tomatoes-person|ricky_gervais|Ricky Gervais}}\n\n{{Ricky Gervais}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Awards for Ricky Gervais\n| list =\n{{British Academy Television Award for Best Comedy Performance}}\n{{BAFTA Los Angeles Britannia Awards}}\n{{EmmyAward ComedyLeadActor 2001-2025}}\n{{GoldenGlobeBestActorTVComedy 1990-2009}}\n{{Satellite Award Best Actor Motion Picture}}\n{{TCA Award for Individual Achievement in Comedy}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gervais, Ricky}}\n[[Category:1961 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century British writers]]\n[[Category:20th-century English comedians]]\n[[Category:20th-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:20th-century atheists]]\n[[Category:21st-century British writers]]\n[[Category:21st-century English comedians]]\n[[Category:21st-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century atheists]]\n[[Category:Alumni of University College London]]\n[[Category:Atheism in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:BAFTA winners (people)]]\n[[Category:Best Musical or Comedy Actor Golden Globe (television) winners]]\n[[Category:British atheism activists]]\n[[Category:British male comedy actors]]\n[[Category:British people of Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:British people of French-Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:British secularists]]\n[[Category:Critics of creationism]]\n[[Category:Critics of religions]]\n[[Category:Cultural critics]]\n[[Category:English atheists]]\n[[Category:English comedy writers]]\n[[Category:English 