le City Hall]]\n|-\n| 5 June 2019\n| [[Newcastle upon Tyne|Newcastle]], [[United Kingdom]]\n| [[Newcastle City Hall]]\n|-\n| 19 June 2019\n| [[Portsmouth]], [[United Kingdom]]\n| [[Portsmouth Guildhall]]\n|-\n| 20 June 2019\n| [[Portsmouth]], [[United Kingdom]]\n| [[Portsmouth Guildhall]]\n|-\n| 26 June 2019\n| [[Cardiff]], [[United Kingdom]]\n| [[Motorpoint Arena Cardiff]]\n|-\n| 27 June 2019\n| [[Cardiff]], [[United Kingdom]]\n| [[Motorpoint Arena Cardiff]]\n|-\n| 5 July 2019\n| [[Amsterdam]], [[Netherlands]]\n| [[AFAS Live]]\n|-\n| 6 July 2019\n| [[Amsterdam]], [[Netherlands]]\n| [[AFAS Live]]\n|-\n| 16 November 2019\n| [[Madrid]], [[Spain]]\n| Palacio Municipal de Congresos de Madrid\n|-\n| 24 November 2019\n| [[Paris]], [[France]]\n| [[Olympia (Paris)]]\n|}\n\n===DVD / Netflix releases===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Notes\n! Shows\n|-\n| 2003 || ''[[Animals (2003 film)|Animals]]'' || DVD release || {{n/a}}\n|-\n| 2004 || ''[[Politics (2004 film)|Politics]]'' || DVD release || {{n/a}}\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[Fame (2007 film)|Fame]]'' || DVD release || {{n/a}}\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Science (film)|Science]]'' || DVD release || 32 shows\n|-\n| 2017\u20132018 || ''Humanity'' || [[Netflix]] Exclusive || 146 shows\n|-\n| 2019\u20132020 || [[SuperNature]] || [[Netflix]] Exclusive || TBD\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Work\n! Result\n|-\n| rowspan=5|2002 || rowspan=2|[[British Academy Television Awards]] || [[British Academy Television Award for Best Situation Comedy|Best Situation Comedy]] || rowspan=19|''[[The Office (UK TV series)|The Office]]'' || {{won}}\n|-\n| [[British Academy Television Award for Best Comedy Performance|Best Comedy Performance]] || {{won}}\n|-\n| [[British Comedy Awards]] || [[British Comedy Awards#2002|Best Comedy Actor]] || {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Broadcasting Press Guild Awards]] || Writer's Award || {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Royal Television Society]] || Best Actor 